article_title: Five Reported Injured in Massachusetts Chemical Plant Explosion
article_text:
NORTH ANDOVER, Mass.—Authorities say a reported explosion at a Dow Chemical plant in northeastern Massachusetts has injured five people and damaged part of the building.

Firefighters, paramedics and police responded to the plant in North Andover at about 2:30 p.m. Thursday.
